---
export let action = "/submit-donation";
---

<section class="donation-container">
  <div class="text-section">
    <h1>Hjemløse har brug for ly.<br />Vi har brug for dig.</h1>
    <p>
      Hos WeShelter arbejder vi for at give hjemløse et trygt sted at sove, et
      varmt måltid og den støtte, de har brug for til at komme videre i livet.
      Ingen fortjener at stå alene – din donation kan give håb, varme og en ny
      begyndelse.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="form-section">
    <form action={action} method="POST" class="donation-form">
      <div class="donation-options">
        <button type="button" class="active">Støt månedligt</button>
        <button type="button">Enkelt donation</button>
      </div>

      <div class="amount-selection">
        <button type="button">60 DKK</button>
        <button type="button">120 DKK</button>
        <button type="button">200 DKK</button>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Andet beløb (DKK)" />
      </div>

      <div class="payment-methods">
        <button type="button">MobilePay</button>
        <button type="button">Betalingsservice</button>
        <button type="button">Betalingskort</button>
      </div>

      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Fornavn" required />
        <input type="text" placeholder="Efternavn" required />
      </div>

      <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required />
      <input type="tel" placeholder="Telefon" required />
      <input type="text" placeholder="Adresse" required />

      <div class="checkbox-group">
        <label><input type="checkbox" /> Ja tak, jeg ønsker skattefradrag</label
        >
        <label><input type="checkbox" required /> Accepter betingelser</label>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="donate-button">STØT</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .donation-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
  }

  .text-section {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 50%;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .form-section {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 50%;
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 2px solid #2a5bd7;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .donation-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .donation-options,
  .amount-selection,
  .payment-methods,
  .input-group,
  .checkbox-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .donate-button {
    background-color: #2a5bd7;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>
